9. Testing Plan
Testing Types
Unit Testing: Testing individual components and functionalities.
Integration Testing: Testing integration points between different systems.
System Testing: Testing the complete system for functionality and performance.
User Acceptance Testing (UAT): Testing by end-users to validate the platform against requirements.
Test Cases
Login Functionality: Test login and registration processes.
Comparison Tools: Test the functionality and accuracy of comparison tools.
Petrol Pump Finder: Test search and location features.
